    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a mistake though. it's like... everything i do just makes things harder for them. i'm like a dark cloud over their lives. i look at them and i just feel so guilty that i'm the one they have to rely on. i feel like i'm poisoning them just by being there.",
